<div class="has-questions">
    <div class="has-questions__content">
        <h3 class="has-questions__heading">
            Остались вопросы?
        </h3>
        <div class="has-questions__text">
            <p>
                Заполните форму и получите консультацию в ближайшее время!
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <form action="/" method="POST" class="has-questions__form" data-need-validation="">
        <div class="has-questions__form-input-wrapper">
            <input type="text" class="text-input text-input--white" required="" name="name" placeholder="Ваше имя">
        </div>
        <div class="has-questions__form-input-wrapper">
            <input type="tel" class="text-input text-input--white js-phone-input" required="" name="phone"
                placeholder="+7 (900) 000-00-00" data-parsley-phone="">
        </div>
        <button class="blue-btn blue-btn--orange has-questions__form-submit">
            Отправить заявку
        </button>
    </form>
</div>